msgid "You recently connected an external monitor or TV to your computer. In this case, whenever |app| opens a new window like the edit metadata window or the conversion dialog, it appears on the second monitor where you dont notice it and so you think |app| has frozen. Disconnect your second monitor and restart calibre."
