msgid "One common cause of failures on OS X is the use of accessibility technologies that are incompatible with the graphics toolkit |app| uses. Try turning off VoiceOver if you have it on. Also go to System Preferences->System->Universal Access and turn off the setting for enabling access for assistive devices in all the tabs."
